    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-cared-for daily driver, offering a perfect balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish with only the slightest imperfections typical of careful road use, and the body panels are straight with consistent gaps. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and odor-free; the upholstery shows minimal wear, and all interior electronics\u2014including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control\u2014operate perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, having benefited from a strict adherence to factory-recommended oil changes and recent brake service. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride without any unusual noises. This car comes complete with a full set of floor mats, two remote key fobs, and a detailed log of its maintenance history, ensuring the next owner can drive away with total confidence.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
