      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated blend of performance and reliability. This unit exhibits consistent mechanical integrity and has been preserved to a high standard, ensuring a premium driving experience. With a documented history of care, this vehicle represents a significant opportunity for the professional seeking dependable luxury and lasting value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
