      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014it's reliable, drives great, and has been well-maintained throughout the time I've owned it. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks sharp on the road. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a test drive, and see how smoothly it handles! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
